@startuml
title LowCortisol - Plan Backend Class Diagram

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false

package "Not implemented in backend" {
  class "Plan backend context" as PlanCandidate
}

package "Frontend module" {
  class Plan
  class PlanFeature
  class Subscription
  class Payment
  class ServiceRequest
}

Plan "1" o-- "*" PlanFeature
Subscription --> Plan
Payment --> Subscription
ServiceRequest --> Subscription
PlanCandidate ..> Plan : future backend candidate

note bottom of PlanCandidate
  The current platform backend does not contain
  a Plan bounded context. Plan is implemented
  in the frontend/product scope.
end note

@enduml
